    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="基于Node-JS的博客系统的设计与实现"><a href="#基于Node-JS的博客系统的设计与实现" class="headerlink" title="基于Node.JS的博客系统的设计与实现"></a>基于Node.JS的博客系统的设计与实现</h1><p>技术栈&amp;框架：</p><p>nodejs: v18.13.0    npm: v9.4.0</p><p>git: v2.35.1</p><p>hexo: v6.3.0</p><p>butterfly：v4.6.1</p><h2 id="1、安装nodejs"><a href="#1、安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="1、安装nodejs"></a>1、安装nodejs</h2><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126222231566.png" alt="image-20230126222231566"></p><p><img src="file:///C:\Users\ADMINI~1\AppData\Local\Temp\ksohtml2764\wps1.jpg" alt="img"></p><h2 id="2、修改缓存、依赖的的存放目录"><a href="#2、修改缓存、依赖的的存放目录" class="headerlink" title="2、修改缓存、依赖的的存放目录"></a>2、修改缓存、依赖的的存放目录</h2><p>环境配置</p><ol><li><p>找到安装nodejs的路径</p></li><li><p>新增 node_global 和 node_cache 文件夹</p></li><li><p>创建完两个空文件夹之后，打开cmd命令窗口，输入</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config set prefix &quot;E:\Environment\NodeJS\node_global&quot;</span><br><span class="line">npm config set cache &quot;E:\Environment\NodeJS\node_cache&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li><p>接下来设置环境变量，关闭cmd窗口，“我的电脑”-右键-“属性”-“高级系统设置”-“高级”-“环境变量” 或者在桌面搜索编辑系统环境变量 </p></li><li><p>相关配置<br>用户变量 path ：E:\Environment\NodeJS\node_global<br>系统变量 NODE_PATH ：E:\Environment\NodeJS\node_modules</p></li></ol><h2 id="3、安装淘宝镜像"><a href="#3、安装淘宝镜像" class="headerlink" title="3、安装淘宝镜像"></a>3、安装淘宝镜像</h2><p>因为原镜像在国外，访问很慢；所以需要安装淘宝镜像</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">安装命令</span></span><br><span class="line">npm config set registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">查询</span></span><br><span class="line">npm config get registry</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126200305130.png" alt="image-20230126200305130"></p><hr><h1 id="安装框架hexo"><a href="#安装框架hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装框架hexo"></a>安装框架hexo</h1><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="安装git"><a href="#安装git" class="headerlink" title="安装git"></a>安装git</h1><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126203219476.png" alt="image-20230126203219476"></p><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126213054666.png" alt="image-20230126213054666"></p><h1 id="github"><a href="#github" class="headerlink" title="github"></a>github</h1><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126213614019.png" alt="image-20230126213614019"></p><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126220844785.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126221211740.png" alt="image-20230126221211740"></p><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126221647739.png" alt=""></p><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126204959208.png" alt="image-20230126204959208"></p><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20230126210535425.png" alt="image-20230126210535425"></p><p